hostname.description: Required. Hostname for the SSH tunnel.

port.description: Port for the SSH tunnel, default value is 22.

username.description: Required. Username for the SSH tunnel.

StaticServiceIpConnectivity.description: Static IP address connectivity. Used when the source database is configured to allow incoming connections from the Datastream public IP addresses for the region specified in the connection profile.

oracleRdbms.description: Oracle RDBMS to enrich with child data objects and metadata.

postgresqlRdbms.description: PostgreSQL RDBMS to enrich with child data objects and metadata.

fullHierarchy.description: Whether to retrieve the full hierarchy of data objects (TRUE) or only the current level (FALSE).

mysqlRdbms.description: MySQL RDBMS to enrich with child data objects and metadata.

connectionProfileName.description: A reference to an existing connection profile.

hierarchyDepth.description: The number of hierarchy levels below the current level to be retrieved.

Route.description: The route resource is the child of the private connection resource, used for defining a route for a private connection.

name.description: Output only. The resource's name.

createTime.description: Output only. The create time of the resource.

updateTime.description: Output only. The update time of the resource.

operations.description: A list of operations that matches the specified filter in the request.

OperationMetadata.description: Represents the metadata of the long-running operation.

statusMessage.description: Output only. Human-readable status of the operation, if any.

createTime.description: Output only. The time the operation was created.

verb.description: Output only. Name of the verb executed by the operation.

requestedCancellation.description: Output only. Identifies whether the user has requested cancellation of the operation. Operations that have successfully been cancelled have Operation.error value with a google.rpc.Status.code of 1, corresponding to `Code.CANCELLED`.

target.description: Output only. Server-defined resource path for the target of the operation.

apiVersion.description: Output only. API version used to start the operation.

endTime.description: Output only. The time the operation finished running.

validationResult.description: Output only. Results of executed validations if there are any.

oracleSchemas.description: Oracle schemas/databases in the database server.

SourceHierarchyDatasets.description: Destination datasets are created so that hierarchy of the destination data objects matches the source hierarchy.

datasetTemplate.description: The dataset template to use for dynamic dataset creation.

ordinalPosition.description: The ordinal position of the column in the table.

nullable.description: Whether or not the column can accept a null value.

primaryKey.description: Whether or not the column represents a primary key.

postgresqlSchemas.description: PostgreSQL schemas in the database server.

schemaFileFormat.description: The schema file format along JSON data files.

compression.description: Compression of the loaded JSON file.

StartBackfillJobRequest.description: Request for manually initiating a backfill job for a specific stream object.

metadata.description: Additional metadata related to the result.

enumDescriptions: Potentially cause issues with the Stream.
Definitely cause issues with the Stream.

code.description: A custom code identifying this specific message.

SingleTargetDataset.description: A single target dataset to which all data will be streamed.

datasetId.description: The dataset ID of the target dataset.

privateConnection.description: Required. A reference to a private connection resource. Format: `projects/{project}/locations/{location}/privateConnections/{name}`

BackfillJob.description: Represents a backfill job on a specific stream object.

lastEndTime.description: Output only. Backfill job's end time.

enumDescriptions: Object backfill job was triggered automatically according to the stream's backfill strategy.
Object backfill job was triggered manually using the dedicated API.

lastStartTime.description: Output only. Backfill job's start time.

enumDescriptions: Backfill job was never started for the stream object (stream has backfill strategy defined as manual or object was explicitly excluded from automatic backfill).
Backfill job will start pending available resources.
Backfill job stopped (next job run will start from beginning).
Backfill job failed (due to an error).
Backfill job failed since the table structure is currently unsupported for backfill.

errors.description: Output only. Errors which caused the backfill job to fail.

username.description: Required. Username for the Oracle connection.

port.description: Port for the Oracle connection, default value is 1521.

password.description: Required. Password for the Oracle connection.

hostname.description: Required. Hostname for the Oracle connection.

databaseService.description: Required. Database for the Oracle connection.
